Package: regress3d
Title: Create 3D Regression Surfaces
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ella", "Foster-Molina", email = "ella.fostermolina@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7455-7221"))
Description: Plot regression surfaces and 
marginal effects in three dimensions. The plots are 'plotly' objects and  
can be customized using functions and arguments 
from the 'plotly' package.
